  <summary>9/27/1996--Introduced.
United States Immigration Court Act of 1996 - Amends the Immigration and Nationality Act to establish the United States Immigration Court, which shall consist of trial and appellate divisions. Sets forth operational, administrative, and jurisdictional provisions. Revises asylum provisions.</summary>
